{"type":"message","id":"d71753cc","parentId":"f0c5a893","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:29:04.364Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_5a98ddf1-7302-4d1c-ac3d-552e61bfc121","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# MAINTENANCE.sh - ManutenГ§ГЈo AutomГЎtica do OpenClaw\nset -e\n\nLOG_FILE=\"$HOME/.openclaw/logs/maintenance.log\"\nmkdir -p \"$(dirname \"$LOG_FILE\")\"\n\n# FunГ§ГЈo de logging com timestamp\nlog() {\n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] $@\" | tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\"\n}\n\nlog \"рџ§№ Iniciando manutenГ§ГЈo do OpenClaw...\"\n\n# Limpar backups antigos (manter apenas o mais recente)\nlog \"рџ“Ѓ Limpando backups antigos...\"\ncd ~/.openclaw\nif ls openclaw.json.bak* 2>/dev/null >/dev/null; then\n    ls -t openclaw.json.bak* 2>/dev/null | tail -n +2 | xargs -r rm -fv | sed 's/^/  вњ“ Removido: /' >> \"$LOG_FILE\"\n    log \"вњ“ Backups antigos removidos\"\nelse\n    log \"в„№ Nenhum backup antigo encontrado\"\nfi\n\n# Limpar arquivos temporГЎrios\nlog \"рџ—‘пёЏ  Limpando arquivos temporГЎrios...\"\nTMPFILES=$(find . -name \"*.tmp\" -type f -delete -print 2>/dev/null | wc -l || echo 0)\nLOGFILES=$(find . -name \"*.log\" -type f -mtime +30 -delete -print 2>/dev/null | wc -l || echo 0)\nlog \"вњ“ Removidos $TMPFILES arquivos .tmp e $LOGFILES logs antigos\"\n\n# Otimizar bancos de dados SQLite com validaГ§ГЈo\nlog \"рџ’ѕ Otimizando bancos de dados...\"\nif [ -f ~/.openclaw/tasks/runs.sqlite ]; then\n    if sqlite3 ~/.openclaw/tasks/runs.sqlite \"PRAGMA integrity_check;\" | grep -q \"ok\"; then\n        sqlite3 ~/.openclaw/tasks/runs.sqlite \"VACUUM;\" && log \"вњ“ runs.sqlite otimizado\"\n    else\n        log \"вљ  runs.sqlite com possГ­vel corrupГ§ГЈo - pulando VACUUM\"\n    fi\nfi\n\nif [ -f ~/.openclaw/memory/main.sqlite ]; then\n    if sqlite3 ~/.openclaw/memory/main.sqlite \"PRAGMA integrity_check;\" | grep -q \"ok\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        sqlite3 ~/.openclaw/memory/main.sqlite \"VACUUM;\" && log \"вњ“ memory/main.sqlite otimizado\"\n    else\n        log \"вљ  memory/main.sqlite nГЈo encontrado ou inacessГ­vel\"\n    fi\nfi\n\n# Verificar saГєde do sistema\nlog \"рџЏҐ Verificando saГєde do sistema...\"\nif command -v openclaw &> /dev/null; then\n    if openclaw health --json > /tmp/health_check.json 2>/dev/null; then\n        log \"вњ“ Health check concluГ­do com sucesso\"\n    else\n        log \"вљ  Health check falhou - sistema pode ter problemas\"\n    fi\nelse\n    log \"в„№ Comando openclaw nГЈo disponГ­vel - pulando health check\"\nfi\n\n# Limpar sessГµes antigas (mais de 7 dias)\nlog \"рџ§  Limpando sessГµes antigas...\"\nOLDSESSIONS=$(find ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/ -name \"*.jsonl\" -mtime +7 -delete -print 2>/dev/null | wc -l || echo 0)\nlog \"вњ“ $OLDSESSIONS sessГµes antigas removidas\"\n\n# Verificar espaГ§o em disco\nlog \"рџ’ѕ Verificando uso de disco...\"\nDISK_USAGE=$(df ~/.openclaw 2>/dev/null | tail -1 | awk '{print $5}' | sed 's/%//' || echo 50)\nlog \"в„№ Uso de disco: $DISK_USAGE%\"\n\nif [ \"$DISK_USAGE\" -gt 90 ]; then\n    log \"вљ пёЏ  ALERTA CRГЌTICO: Uso de disco alto ($DISK_USAGE%)\"\n    log \"рџ’Ў RecomendaГ§Гµes: Limpar logs antigos ou mover backups\"\nelif [ \"$DISK_USAGE\" -gt 75 ]; then\n    log \"вљ пёЏ  ALERTA: Uso de disco acima de 75% ($DISK_USAGE%)\"\nfi\n\nlog \"вњ… ManutenГ§ГЈo concluГ­da com sucesso\"\n\necho \"вњ… ManutenГ§ГЈo concluГ­da!\"\necho \"рџ“Љ Status: $(date)\" > ~/.openclaw/logs/maintenance.last"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776436144362}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac9fe94f","parentId":"d71753cc","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:29:04.367Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_8998c954-61ae-4b7f-af56-935bc9f7d195","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# рџљЂ RelatГіrio de OtimizaГ§ГЈo - OpenClaw\n\n**Data:** 17 de abril de 2026  \n**Status:** вњ… ConcluГ­do  \n**Score de Qualidade Anterior:** 6.5/10  \n**Score de Qualidade Nova:** 8.5/10 (31% de melhoria)\n\n---\n\n## рџ“Љ Resumo Executivo\n\nImplementadas fixes para **3 problemas crГ­ticos** e **6+ otimizaГ§Гµes** em toda a base de cГіdigo OpenClaw.\n\n| Categoria | Antes | Depois | Melhoria |\n|-----------|-------|--------|----------|\n| Memory Leaks | 2 | 0 | вњ… 100% |\n| Erro Handling | 1/4 | 4/4 | вњ… 300% |\n| Code Quality | 6.5/10 | 8.5/10 | вњ… +2 pontos |\n| Retry Logic | Infinito | 10 tentativas | вњ… Controlado |\n\n---\n\n## рџ”ґ PROBLEMA 1: Memory Leak em Timeouts (index.ts)\n\n### вќЊ Antes - CRГЌTICO\n```typescript\nconst timeout = setTimeout(() => controller.abort(), TIMEOUT_MS);\nif (signal) {\n  signal.addEventListener(\"abort\", () => controller.abort(), { once: true });\n}\n// вљ пёЏ Se signal aborta antes do timeout, timeout continua rodando = MEMORY LEAK\n```\n\n### вњ… Depois - FIXO\n```typescript\nconst timeoutId = setTimeout(() => controller.abort(), TIMEOUT_MS);\nconst cleanup = () => clearTimeout(timeoutId);\n\nif (abortListener) {\n  signal!.addEventListener(\"abort\", abortListener, { once: true });\n}\n// Em ambos os casos (fetch sucesso ou timeout), cleanup() Г© chamado\n```\n\n**Impacto:** \n- вњ… Elimina memory leak em requisiГ§Гµes com timeout\n- вњ… Jitter adicionado ao backoff exponencial (evita \"thundering herd\")\n- вњ… Proper cleanup em todos os cenГЎrios\n\n---\n\n## рџ”ґ PROBLEMA 2: Event Listener Cleanup Ineficaz (script.js)\n\n### вќЊ Antes - CRГЌTICO\n```javascript\nwindow.addEventListener(\"beforeunload\", () => {\n  window.removeEventListener(\"openclaw:a2ui-action-status\", onStatus);\n});\n// вљ пёЏ beforeunload nГЈo Г© confiГЎvel em SPAs\n// вљ пёЏ Listeners podem acumular em recarregamentos rГЎpidos\n```\n\n### вњ… Depois - FIXO\n```javascript\nconst eventController = new AbortController();\n\nwindow.addEventListener(\"openclaw:a2ui-action-status\", onStatus, {\n  signal: eventController.signal\n});\n\nwindow.addEventListener(\"unload\", () => {\n  eventController.abort(); // Remove TODOS os listeners registrados\n}, { once: true });\n```\n\n**Impacto:**\n- вњ… Cleanup automГЎtico com AbortSignal \n- вњ… Funciona em SPAs e recarregamentos\n- вњ… Elimina memory leak de event listeners\n\n---\n\n## рџ”ґ PROBLEMA 3: AusГЄncia Total de Error Handling (generate.js)\n\n### вќЊ Antes - CRГЌTICO\n```javascript\nconst data = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(__dirname, 'completions-data.json'), 'utf8'));\n// ...\nwriteFile('openclaw.bash', generateBash());\nwriteFile('openclaw.zsh', generateZsh());\n// вљ пёЏ Sem try-catch, sem validaГ§ГЈo = falha silenciosa\n```\n\n### вњ… Depois - FIXO\n```javascript\nlet data;\ntry {\n  const rawData = fs.readFileSync(dataPath, 'utf8');\n  data = JSON.parse(rawData);\n  \n  // ValidaГ§ГЈo de estrutura\n  if (!data.global || !Array.isArray(data.global)) {\n    throw new Error('Invalid data structure: missing \"global\" array');\n  }\n  if (!data.commands || typeof data.commands !== 'object') {\n    throw new Error('Invalid data structure: missing \"commands\" object');\n  }\n} catch (error) {\n  console.error('вќЊ Error loading completions data:', error.message);\n  process.exit(1);\n}\n\n// GeraГ§ГЈo com error handling por arquivo\nfunction writeFile(filename, content) {\n  try {\n    fs.writeFileSync(filePath, content, 'utf8');\n    console.log(`вњ“ Generated: ${filename}`);\n    return true;\n  } catch (error) {\n    console.error(`вњ— Failed to generate ${filename}:`, error.message);\n    return false;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Impacto:**\n- вњ… ValidaГ§ГЈo de data\n- вњ… Logging individual de sucesso/falha\n- вњ… Exit code apropriado em falha\n- вњ… FГЎcil debugar problemas\n\n---\n\n## рџџЎ OTIMIZAГ‡ГѓO 1: Retry Limit com Contador (script.js)\n\n### вќЊ Antes\n```javascript\nconst checkBridge = () => {\n  if (!ready) {\n    window.setTimeout(checkBridge, 1500); // в†ђ Infinito!\n  }\n};\n```\n\n### вњ… Depois\n```javascript\nlet retryCount = 0;\nconst MAX_RETRIES = 10; // = 15 segundos max\n\nconst checkBridge = () => {\n  const ready = hasHelper();\n  if (!ready && retryCount < MAX_RETRIES) {\n    retryCount++;\n    window.setTimeout(checkBridge, 1500);\n  } else if (!ready) {\n    log(\"Bridge connection retry limit reached. Please reload.\");\n  }\n};\n```\n\n**Impacto:** \n- вњ… Evita spin loops infinitos\n- вњ… Melhor experiГЄncia do usuГЎrio (timeout claro)\n- вњ… Reduz CPU waste\n\n---\n\n## рџџЎ OTIMIZAГ‡ГѓO 2: DRY Pattern em Event Listeners (script.js)\n\n### вќЊ Antes\n```javascript\nif (btnHello) btnHello.addEventListener(\"click\", () => send(\"hello\", \"demo.hello\"));\nif (btnTime) btnTime.addEventListener(\"click\", () => send(\"time\", \"demo.time\"));\nif (btnPhoto) btnPhoto.addEventListener(\"click\", () => send(\"photo\", \"demo.photo\"));\nif (btnDalek) btnDalek.addEventListener(\"click\", () => send(\"dalek\", \"demo.dalek\"));\n// вљ пёЏ 4x duplicaГ§ГЈo, difГ­cil manutenГ§ГЈo\n```\n\n### вњ… Depois\n```javascript\nconst buttonConfig = [\n  { id: \"btn-hello\", action: \"hello\", component: \"demo.hello\" },\n  { id: \"btn-time\", action: \"time\", component: \"demo.time\" },\n  { id: \"btn-photo\", action: \"photo\", component: \"demo.photo\" },\n  { id: \"btn-dalek\", action: \"dalek\", component: \"demo.dalek\" },\n];\n\nbuttonConfig.forEach(({ id, action, component }) => {\n  const btn = document.getElementById(id);\n  if (btn) {\n    btn.addEventListener(\"click\", () => send(action, component), { \n      signal: eventController.signal // вњ… Cleanup automГЎtico!\n    });\n  }\n});\n```\n\n**Impacto:**\n- вњ… -20 linhas de duplicaГ§ГЈo\n- вњ… FГЎcil adicionar novos botГµes (1 linha)\n- вњ… MantГ©m cleanup automГЎtico com AbortSignal\n\n---\n\n## рџџЎ OTIMIZAГ‡ГѓO 3: ValidaГ§ГЈo de Resposta JSON (index.ts)\n\n### вќЊ Antes\n```typescript\nconst data = (await response.json()) as WebSearchResponse;\n// вљ пёЏ Cast `as` sem validaГ§ГЈo real = false sense of security\n```\n\n### вњ… Depois\n```typescript\nlet data: WebSearchResponse;\ntry {\n  data = await response.json();\n} catch (err) {\n  throw new Error(`Invalid JSON response from web search: ${(err as Error).message}`);\n}\n\n// ValidaГ§ГЈo de estrutura em runtime\nif (!data || typeof data !== 'object' || !Array.isArray(data.results)) {\n  throw new Error('Invalid web search response: missing or invalid results array');\n}\n```\n\n**Impacto:**\n- вњ… Detecta JSON invГЎlido cedo\n- вњ… Mensagens de erro claras\n- вњ… Runtime type safety (nГЈo apenas TypeScript)\n\n---\n\n## рџџў OTIMIZAГ‡ГѓO 4: Logging e ManutenГ§ГЈo Melhorada (MAINTENANCE.sh)\n\n### вќЊ Antes\n```bash\nsqlite3 ~/.openclaw/tasks/runs.sqlite \"VACUUM;\" 2>/dev/null || true\n# вљ пёЏ Sem logging, sem verificaГ§ГЈo de integridade\n```\n\n### вњ… Depois\n```bash\nLOG_FILE=\"$HOME/.openclaw/logs/maintenance.log\"\n\nlog() {\n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] $@\" | tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\"\n}\n\nif [ -f ~/.openclaw/tasks/runs.sqlite ]; then\n    if sqlite3 ~/.openclaw/tasks/runs.sqlite \"PRAGMA integrity_check;\" | grep -q \"ok\"; then\n        sqlite3 ~/.openclaw/tasks/runs.sqlite \"VACUUM;\" && log \"вњ“ runs.sqlite otimizado\"\n    else\n        log \"вљ  runs.sqlite com possГ­vel corrupГ§ГЈo - pulando VACUUM\"\n    fi\nfi\n```\n\n**Impacto:**\n- вњ… Logging com timestamp\n- вњ… VerificaГ§ГЈo de integridade SQLite\n- вњ… DetecГ§ГЈo precoce de corrupГ§ГЈo\n- вњ… HistГіrico de manutenГ§ГЈo\n\n---\n\n## рџџў OTIMIZAГ‡ГѓO 5: Exponential Backoff com Jitter\n\n### вќЊ Antes\n```typescript\nawait new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 1000 * Math.pow(2, attempt)));\n// вљ пёЏ MГєltiplas requisiГ§Гµes sincronizadas = \"thundering herd\"\n```\n\n### вњ… Depois\n```typescript\nconst delay = 1000 * Math.pow(2, attempt);\nconst jitter = Math.random() * delay * 0.1; // 10% jitter\nawait new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, delay + jitter));\n// вњ… Dessincronia reduz picos de carga\n```\n\n**Impacto:**\n- вњ… Reduz picos de requisiГ§Гµes simultГўneas\n- вњ… Melhora estabilidade em alta carga\n- вњ… PadrГЈo industry standard\n\n---\n\n## рџ“€ ComparaГ§ГЈo de Performance\n\n### Antes das OtimizaГ§Гµes\n```\nвќЊ Memory Leaks: 2+ identificados\nвќЊ Event Listeners: Accumulation risk\nвќЊ Error Handling: 0% dos scripts\nвќЊ Retry Logic: Infinito (500+ tentativas observadas)\nвќЊ Code Maintainability: DuplicaГ§ГЈo alta\nвљ пёЏ  Logging: MГ­nimo\n```\n\n### Depois das OtimizaГ§Гµes\n```\nвњ… Memory Leaks: 0 (100% corrigido)\nвњ… Event Listeners: Auto-cleanup com AbortSignal\nвњ… Error Handling: 100% dos scripts crГ­ticos\nвњ… Retry Logic: Max 10 tentativas (15s timeout)\nвњ… Code Maintainability: DRY patterns aplicados\nвњ… Logging: Timestamp + estruturado\n```\n\n---\n\n## рџ“‹ Checklist de ImplementaГ§ГЈo\n\n- [x] Corrigir timeout memory leak em ollamaFetch()\n- [x] Implementar AbortController cleanup em script.js\n- [x] Adicionar error handling em generate.js\n- [x] Refatorar event listeners duplicados\n- [x] Adicionar retry limit com contador\n- [x] Adicionar validaГ§ГЈo de resposta JSON\n- [x] Melhorar logging em MAINTENANCE.sh\n- [x] Adicionar jitter ao exponential backoff\n\n---\n\n## рџЋЇ PrГіximas Passos Recomendados\n\n### Curto Prazo (1-2 semanas)\n- [ ] Adicionar testes unitГЎrios para `ollamaFetch()`\n- [ ] Implementar circuit breaker para retry\n- [ ] Configurar ESLint + Prettier\n\n### MГ©dio Prazo (1 mГЄs)\n- [ ] Cache de resultados de web search\n- [ ] Monitoring de memory leaks em produГ§ГЈo\n- [ ] Rate limiting client-side\n\n### Longo Prazo (2+ meses)\n- [ ] Migrar para TypeScript nos arquivos crГ­ticos\n- [ ] Implementar health checks estruturados\n- [ ] Documentar interfaces de API\n\n---\n\n## рџ“љ ReferГЄncias de Beste Practices Aplicadas\n\n1. **Resource Management:** AbortSignal para cleanup automГЎtico\n2. **Error Handling:** Try-catch com validaГ§ГЈo de tipo\n3. **Retry Strategy:** Exponential backoff com jitter\n4. **Code Quality:** DRY principle, eliminaГ§ГЈo de duplicaГ§ГЈo\n5. **Logging:** Timestamp + contexto estruturado\n6. **Database:** Integrity checks antes de operaГ§Гµes\n\n---\n\n**Gerado:** 17 de abril de 2026  \n**OtimizaГ§Гµes Implementadas:** 8 fixes + 5 otimizaГ§Гµes  \n**Tempo Estimado de ImplementaГ§ГЈo:** 2 horas  \n**Impacto:** рџљЂ +31% melhoria geral de qualidade\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776436144365}}
