{"type":"message","id":"7d7492d1","parentId":"f3bddca7","timestamp":"2026-04-17T14:44:06.379Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_38f30029-37ff-4683-b6b5-0f9644332be0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# вњ… SETUP COMPLETO - Score 8.7/10 (P0)\n\n**Data:** 17 de abril de 2026  \n**Status:** вњ… CONCLUГЌDO  \n**Tempo Investido:** ~2 horas  \n**Testes:** 61/61 passando вњ…\n\n---\n\n## рџ“Љ Score de Qualidade\n\n| MГ©trica | Antes | Depois | Ganho |\n|---------|-------|--------|-------|\n| **Qualidade Geral** | 8.5/10 | 8.7/10 | +0.2 |\n| **Cobertura de Testes** | 0% | 61 testes | рџљЂ |\n| **SeguranГ§a** | вљ пёЏ 40% | рџџў 60% | +20% |\n| **DevOps** | 20% | 50% | +30% |\n| **Code Quality** | 6.5/10 | 7.5/10 | +1.0 |\n\n**PrГіximo Marco:** 9.4/10 (P1 = 19h)\n\n---\n\n## рџЋЇ O Que Foi Implementado (P0)\n\n### вњ… Testes Automatizados - 61 Testes\n```\ncanvas/script.spec.ts              15 testes вњ“\ncompletions/generate.spec.ts       17 testes вњ“  \nextensions/openclaw-web-search/    29 testes вњ“\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nTotal:                             61 testes вњ“\n```\n\n#### Coverage por Arquivo:\n- вњ… **script.js** - Event listeners, cleanup, retry logic\n- вњ… **generate.js** - Data validation, error handling\n- вњ… **index.ts** - Timeout management, backoff, JSON validation\n\n### вњ… Geramento de Ambiente\n- `package.json` com scripts de teste + lint\n- `vitest.config.ts` com coverage reporter\n- `tsconfig.json` com strict mode\n- `.env.example` com variГЎveis seguras\n\n### вњ… DevOps & Code Quality\n- `.eslintrc.json` - Linting configurado\n- `.prettierrc` - FormataГ§ГЈo padronizada\n- `.gitignore` - ProteГ§ГЈo de credentials\n- NPM scripts: `test`, `lint`, `format`\n\n### вњ… DocumentaГ§ГЈo\n- ConfiguraГ§ГЈo clara em arquivo de exemplo\n- Estrutura de testes bem organizada\n- Comments explicando validaГ§Гµes\n\n---\n\n## рџ§Є Testes P0 Implementados\n\n### 1. Timeout & Memory Leaks (7 testes вњ“)\n```\nвњ“ should clear timeout on successful fetch\nвњ“ should clear timeout on fetch error\nвњ“ should not create memory leak from orphaned timeouts\nвњ“ should abort fetch when timeout expires\nвњ“ should respects external AbortSignal\nвњ“ should cleanup listener when external signal aborts\nвњ“ should cleanup timeout even if external signal aborts first\n```\n\n### 2. Retry Logic & Backoff (6 testes вњ“)\n```\nвњ“ should attempt retries up to MAX_RETRIES\nвњ“ should apply exponential backoff\nвњ“ should add jitter to exponential backoff\nвњ“ should prevent thundering herd with jitter\nвњ“ should fail after MAX_RETRIES attempts\n```\n\n### 3. ValidaГ§ГЈo JSON & Query (11 testes вњ“)\n```\nвњ“ should validate response is valid JSON\nвњ“ should catch invalid JSON\nвњ“ should validate response structure (has results array)\nвњ“ should reject missing results property\nвњ“ should accept empty results array\nвњ“ should validate result items have required fields\nвњ“ should reject empty query\nвњ“ should reject query with less than 3 characters\nвњ“ should accept valid queries\nвњ“ should trim whitespace from query\n(+ 1 more)\n```\n\n### 4. Event Listeners & DOM (15 testes вњ“)\n```\nвњ“ should limit retry attempts to MAX_RETRIES\nвњ“ should not retry infinitely\nвњ“ should report when retry limit is reached\nвњ“ should allow adding multiple listeners\nвњ“ should support AbortController for cleanup\nвњ“ should cleanup listeners on abort\nвњ“ should use once:true for robust cleanup\nвњ“ should map buttons with configuration object\n(+ 7 mais)\n```\n\n### 5. Error Handling & Messaging (8 testes вњ“)\n```\nвњ“ should provide clear timeout error message\nвњ“ should provide clear auth error message\nвњ“ should provide clear unavailable service error\nвњ“ should provide HTTP status error message\nвњ“ should truncate long content to MAX_LENGTH\nвњ“ should preserve short content without truncation\nвњ“ should format search results correctly\nвњ“ should handle send action errors gracefully\n```\n\n---\n\n## рџ“Ѓ Estrutura de Arquivos Criados\n\n```\n/home/voide/.openclaw/\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ package.json              # Scripts npm (test, lint, format)\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ vitest.config.ts         # ConfiguraГ§ГЈo de testes com coverage\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ tsconfig.json            # Strict TypeScript config\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ .eslintrc.json           # Linting rules\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ .prettierrc               # FormataГ§ГЈo\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ .gitignore               # ProteГ§ГЈo de credentials\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ .env.example             # Exemplo de variГЎveis\nв”‚\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ canvas/\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ script.spec.ts       # 15 testes DOM + cleanup\nв”њв”Ђв”Ђ completions/\nв”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ generate.spec.ts     # 17 testes validaГ§ГЈo/geraГ§ГЈo\nв””в”Ђв”Ђ extensions/openclaw-web-search/\n    в””в”Ђв”Ђ index.spec.ts        # 29 testes timeout/retry/JSON\n```\n\n---\n\n## рџљЂ Como Usar\n\n### Rodar Testes\n```bash\nnpm test                   # Rodar uma vez\nnpm run test:watch        # Watch mode\nnpm run test:ui           # Visual UI\nnpm run test:coverage     # Coverage report\n```\n\n### Linting & FormataГ§ГЈo\n```bash\nnpm run lint              # Verificar linting\nnpm run lint:fix          # Corrigir automГЎtico\nnpm run format            # Formatar cГіdigo\nnpm run format:check      # Verificar formataГ§ГЈo\n```\n\n### Ver Cobertura\n```bash\nnpm run test:coverage\n# Gera: coverage/index.html\n```\n\n---\n\n## рџ“€ PrГіxico Passo: P1 (19h)\n\nPara chegar a **9.4/10**, faltam:\n\n### SeguranГ§a (3h)\n- [ ] Rotacionar credenciais (GitHub token hardcoded)\n- [ ] Implementar .env.local + dotenv\n- [ ] ValidaГ§ГЈo com Zod\n\n### DevOps (7h)\n- [ ] ESLint fixes automГЎticos\n- [ ] GitHub Actions CI/CD  \n- [ ] Pre-commit hooks\n- [ ] Prettier formatting\n\n### Tipos (5h)\n- [ ] TypeScript strict mode\n- [ ] Remover `as` casts sem validaГ§ГЈo\n- [ ] JSDoc generation\n\n### Arquitetura (4h)\n- [ ] Refactor com Repository Pattern\n- [ ] SeparaГ§ГЈo de concerns\n- [ ] Camadas bem definidas\n\n---\n\n## вњЁ Checklist ConcluГ­do (P0)\n\n- [x] Setup Vitest com coverage\n- [x] 61 testes implementados e passando\n- [x] Timeout memory leak validado\n- [x] Retry logic com jitter testado\n- [x] Event listener cleanup testado\n- [x] JSON validation testado\n- [x] .env.example com secrets\n- [x] ESLint configurado\n- [x] Prettier configurado\n- [x] .gitignore para credentials\n- [x] NPM scripts: test, lint, format\n- [x] tsconfig.json com strict mode\n\n---\n\n## рџЋЇ Timeline atГ© 10/10\n\n```\nвњ… Seg - P0 Testes (10h)      в†’ 8.5 вћњ 8.7\nрџџЎ Ter-Qua - P1 DevOps (12h)  в†’ 8.7 вћњ 9.2\nрџџЎ Qui-Sex - P1 Tipos (7h)    в†’ 9.2 вћњ 9.4\nвЏі PrГіx Seg - P2 Polimento (10h) в†’ 9.4 вћњ 10.0 вњЁ\n```\n\n---\n\n## рџ“Љ Impacto nos 3 Problemas CrГ­ticos\n\n| Problema | Status | Teste | Validado |\n|----------|--------|-------|----------|\n| Memory Leak Timeout | вњ… FIXO | `timeout cleanup` | вњ“ |\n| Event Cleanup Ineficaz | вњ… FIXO | `AbortController` | вњ“ |\n| Sem Error Handling | вњ… FIXO | `try-catch validation` | вњ“ |\n\n---\n\n**Criado:** 17 de Abril de 2026  \n**PrГіximo Marco:** 9.2/10 com P1  \n**Objetivo Final:** 10/10 em 1 semana\n\nрџљЂ **VocГЄ estГЎ no caminho certo!**\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776437046377}}
